generatedPrompts.backCover: A minimalist and serene watercolor illustration on a textured paper background. In the upper-left corner, a single, tiny, colorful party hat, identical to the one from the front cover, rests beside a delicate, translucent bubble. The background is a soft, flowing watercolor wash of gentle blues and warm browns with visible organic paint bleeds and artistic brush strokes. The bottom-right corner, approximately 1 inch square, is left completely blank and white. The entire design is full-bleed, extending to all edges except the designated blank corner. Flat 2D artwork.
generatedPrompts.frontCover: A charming watercolor illustration of a sophisticated capybara wearing a tiny, tilted party hat and a monocle. The capybara is lounging majestically in a teacup that is slightly too small for it, causing a comical overflow of tea. Floating around the teacup are a few delicate, translucent bubbles and a single, wayward piece of confetti. In the center, in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "happy birthday, you magnificent creature". The entire scene is rendered in a lighthearted, cartoonish style with soft, flowing watercolor washes of warm browns, gentle blues, and a pop of festive color for the hat, set against a textured paper background with visible organic paint bleeds and artistic brush strokes. Flat 2D artwork.
